DISCOVER
========

GET /discover
-------------
params:
    - offset = int (Default 0)
    - limit = int (Default 30)	
  	- lat = latitude (float)
  	- lng = longitude (float)
  	- city = string (city name)
  	- cc = string (two-letter country code)
  	- includePhotos = 1/0 (default is 1)
  	- numPhotos = int (default 6)
  	- filter = comma-separated list (trending, naerby, favorited, contributed, friendsFavorited, friendsContributed)

notes:
	- GET /users/{id}/discover forwards here > deprecate duplicate endpoint
	- API Version: 2.2.0

todos:
	- better pagination
	- introduce fields

GET /discover/albums
--------------------
    - offset = int (Default 0)
    - limit = int (Default 30)	
  	- lat = latitude (float)
  	- lng = longitude (float)
  	- includePhotos = 1/0 (default is 0)
  	- numPhotos = int (default 10)
  	- includeContributors = 1/0 (default 0)
  	- includeLikers = 1/0 (default is 0)
  	- filter = comma-separated list (trending, naerby, favorited, contributed, friendsFavorited, friendsContributed)
  	- detailed = 1/0 (default 0)

notes:
	- requires authenticated user
	- GET /users/{id}/discoverAlbums forwards here > deprecate duplicate endpoint
	- eventually deduplicate code from GET /discover

todos:
	- better pagination
	- introduce fields
	- album favoriters instead of album likers
	- standardized defaults (For fields/sub-fields)
